I’m considering how to approach this. It seems like using parallel processes might not be the best idea right now, especially because of the git safe directory environment setup and the same manifest. Instead, I think it would be better to use distinct temporary paths. That way, I can ensure everything runs smoothly without any conflicts. It’s all about keeping things organized and efficient!
